      "id": 8,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Drill-down path\n\n1. **Live trace detail:** open Aspire at `http://localhost:18888`.\n2. **Workspace attribution:** open Real Workspace Usage.\n3. **Context and AIU:** open Context and Cost.\n4. **Model labels and sessions:** open Sessions and Model Labels.\n5. **Data quality:** open Data Quality before presenting any metric.\n6. **Prompt improvement:** open Developer Coach.\n\nRaw prompts, tool arguments, and tool results stay local by default. Azure receives sanitized telemetry and rollups. AIU is operational telemetry, not official billing."
      }
    }
